      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-cnf-imp-000      thru acc-cnf-imp-999        .
           if        w-cnt-tus-acc-key    =    "E"
                     move  spaces         to   w-cnt-tus-acc-key
                     go to acc-key-reg-100.
