      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se valore attuale uguale a precedente :     *
      *                  * oltre                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test                                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-are-ges        =    w-sav-are-ges
                     go to acc-are-ges-800.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Normalizzazione tipo documento          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-tip-doc          .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-tip-doc-des      .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-tip-doc-sgl      .
           move      zero                 to   w-tes-tip-doc-ngi      .
           move      zero                 to   w-tes-tip-doc-dpz      .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-tip-doc-key      .
