      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tip-doc-999.
       acc-tip-doc-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Bollettazione                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Accettazione tipo documento                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tip-doc-bol-000  thru acc-tip-doc-bol-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tip-doc-999.
       acc-tip-doc-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ordini clienti                                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Accettazione tipo documento                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tip-doc-orc-000  thru acc-tip-doc-orc-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tip-doc-999.
       acc-tip-doc-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ordini fornitori                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Accettazione tipo documento                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   acc-tip-doc-orf-000  thru acc-tip-doc-orf-999    .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tip-doc-999.
       acc-tip-doc-999.
